{%- comment -%}
  Reusable "Log in to see pricing" CTA. Renders wherever a price
  would normally render for logged-out visitors. Keeps the wording
  and link target consistent across card, PDP, search, cart, etc.

  Inputs (optional):
    - block_modifier : 'small' | '' (default '')
                       'small' renders a smaller version for tight
                       slots like search autocomplete results.
{%- endcomment -%}
<a
  href="{{ routes.account_login_url }}"
  class="misc-price-cta{% if block_modifier == 'small' %} misc-price-cta--small{% endif %}"
>
  Log in to see pricing
</a>
